{"tid":1804644,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇估計武漢爆發病毒感染　籲毋須恐慌","createTime":"2019-12-31T06:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T07:00:52.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c49ec998a7e4f87a6b8d648bab20871b68a0c8","tid":1804644,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:46:23.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇相信，武漢正爆發病毒感染，陸續會有更多感染個案，認為香港有對抗病毒的經驗，市民暫時毋須恐慌。 <br />\n<br />\n袁國勇：「同一時間，同一地點，突然有這樣多病例，應該是有爆發發生，因現在是冬天，最大機會是病毒感染。他們已檢驗過，因此已知的呼吸道病毒，應該已經驗過否則也不會說不明原因，所以暫時應該向不明原因方向推測，毋須太恐慌，因為我們已知玩法，最重要是追蹤、隔離、醫治。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375069&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375069%26refer%3DShare&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJqQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=dc9b71e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375069%26refer%3DShare&h=eff52c09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375069&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"b34fe122e707d948b11443fc7d1304a49141d0c4","tid":1804644,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"德美聯署整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"1ea054c603d6edb4f9d4f9d5066c612b0d843295","tid":1804644,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"掟條撚樣上去啦屌"},{"pid":"41d6921a2e8922f00083451232e41f298d11d02f","tid":1804644,"uid":108757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"驗過但驗完唔知係咩，跟住叫人唔好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e4830b147b6cc0ac6c1e2f829df6cd6d88c6cf","tid":1804644,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"話到明不明原因都仲叫人不要擔憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a427ae2a4bce158babcef69b732fee11ffb6d72c","tid":1804644,"uid":279284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"驗完知係乜有鬼用咩<br />\n班蝗只會亂咁食藥食抗生素<br />\n啲細菌病毒只會越來越勁 越來越難醫"}]}